title: Adelpha Pleated Satin Maxi Dress
description: Featuring Sunray Pleats   Not just your usual pleats - sunray pleating is an intricate, time-intensive form of pleating that begins with smaller, finer pleats at the waistline, before radiating outwards in wider folds, just like the rays of the sun.
